                    <desc type="abstract" xml:lang="en" corresp="http://syriaca.org/geo http://syriaca.org/johnofephesus http://syriaca.org/johnofephesus/places">
                        <quote source="#bib226-1">The Monastery of Qarṭmin began long before its official foundation date of 397.</quote>
